{"tid":380644,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"我係新牌仔，架車用老豆名出保險，如果撞車出事會點？？？","createTime":"2017-08-30T09:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T15:25:02.000Z","uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88efe39cfc7d3fb82bbb14ecf6aa6499c4a31420","tid":380644,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:35:29.000Z","msg":"正常黎講，<br />\n架新車用我名出保險（三保），<br />\n咁撞車撞到人果陣，d 醫藥費就保險公司賠<br />\n呢個都係香港法例要司機有三保既原意，可以保障第三者<br />\n<br />\n但假如我用老豆名出三保<br />\n撞到人果陣，咁要點處理？<br />\n要我自己出錢賠？<br />\n呢個算唔算係香港法例既bug ? 保障第3者fail wor"},{"pid":"f5b5d04f8a812d6567b0622bfc27db266373f50b","tid":380644,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"保險有冇只限指定司機<br />\n如果冇就俾多d墊底"},{"pid":"697c2ab0a9acf4d4b29a1dc0785ff3e94530d528","tid":380644,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"如果係只限落名司機<br />\n就會拉你冇三保"},{"pid":"f70b91e53b5f77ffbceeb9eae27bbea747d0dc76","tid":380644,"uid":98904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"一係你老竇份保險加你名，或者睇保險保唔保UNNAMED DRIVER，保就俾墊底<br />\n<br />\n唔保你就仆街鳥"},{"pid":"da683b02c1a3f8b5d41487fac6750da0c8a4671d","tid":380644,"uid":48078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係只限落名司機<br />\n就會拉你冇三保</blockquote><br />\n好似會拉埋老豆 明知冇三保仲借車比你<br />\n或者你承認偷車"},{"pid":"c61d8ce6218527faef1d48f5657c0c2d86284c76","tid":380644,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"如果撞到你老豆會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2ec1031257e16518061a18502380a51a289766","tid":380644,"uid":85557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果撞到你老豆會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個老豆撞到入廠兼比人拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0860a3653ff6c2676c636103c3cb802d0a820eca","tid":380644,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係你老竇份保險加你名，或者睇保險保唔保UNNAMED DRIVER，保就俾墊底<br />\n<br />\n唔保你就仆街鳥</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a012b42b36110dad958abba3ea6fc446a83d74","tid":380644,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"正如上面講，首先睇有無named driver only clause，如果無，再睇有無話車主唔凖借車俾唔夠牌/歲嘅司機。都無嘅就無問題，只爭在如果涉及財物損失嘅墊底費高低<br />\n<br />\n如果中咗都唔怕，法例同車保局協議都會要求保險賠先，保險會追返你老豆"},{"pid":"8d247eb96b60f356b360f71b704d40a3a336a77b","tid":380644,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果撞到你老豆會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個老豆撞到入廠兼比人拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直入羈留病房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c12ad1882dbdc8d8ae4234579213ac1a003d94","tid":380644,"uid":113021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果撞到你老豆會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個老豆撞到入廠兼比人拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果當時坐側邊既老母證明老豆係亂衝出緊路呢？"},{"pid":"f42e546bd6fb7a269e59988f43e94538058b876a","tid":380644,"uid":113021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果撞到你老豆會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個老豆撞到入廠兼比人拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果當時坐側邊既老母證明老豆係亂衝出馬路呢？</blockquote>"}]}